1. Problem Statement: a.
                        - The hectic process of finding the blood(donor)
                        - Finding appropriate place to donate blood.
                         
                      b.
                        - The project aims at creating a secure bridge the donor, needy and hospitals and various 
                        oganisations through a web portal.
                        - Introduced the concept of donor points.
                        
                      c.
                        - The concept of donor points aims at encouraging the donor to donate blood by giving him/er the
                        security of blood when s/he is in need.
                        - Donor can get the notification about the various blood camps being held in the nearby areas.
                        - Hospitals can the donor area-wise. 
                        d.
